{
  "id": "mixed-computed-overview",
  "name": "Mixed Computed Fields Overview",
  "category": "computed",
  "summary": "Comprehensive example combining arithmetic, ternary conditions, and SUM aggregation in one form",
  "whenToUse": [
    "Reference form demonstrating all computed field patterns in a single example",
    "Testing or validating that the calculation engine handles diverse expressions"
  ],
  "dataSchema": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "x": {
        "type": "number",
        "title": "X"
      },
      "y": {
        "type": "number",
        "title": "Y"
      },
      "z": {
        "type": "number",
        "title": "Z"
      },
      "arr": {
        "type": "array",
        "items": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "c3": {
              "type": "number",
              "title": "C3"
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "total": {
        "type": "string",
        "format": "computed",
        "description": "#/properties/x * #/properties/y + #/properties/z"
      },
      "condition": {
        "type": "string",
        "format": "computed",
        "description": "#/properties/x > 10 ? #/properties/y : #/properties/z"
      },
      "sumC3": {
        "type": "string",
        "format": "computed",
        "description": "SUM(#/properties/arr/c3)"
      }
    }
  },
  "uiSchema": {
    "type": "VerticalLayout",
    "elements": [
      {
        "type": "Control",
        "scope": "#/properties/x"
      },
      {
        "type": "Control",
        "scope": "#/properties/y"
      },
      {
        "type": "Control",
        "scope": "#/properties/z"
      },
      {
        "type": "Control",
        "scope": "#/properties/arr",
        "label": "Array of objects"
      },
      {
        "type": "Control",
        "label": "Total (x × y + z)",
        "scope": "#/properties/total"
      },
      {
        "type": "Control",
        "label": "Condition (if x > 10 then y else z)",
        "scope": "#/properties/condition"
      },
      {
        "type": "Control",
        "label": "Sum of C3",
        "scope": "#/properties/sumC3"
      }
    ]
  },
  "notes": [
    "Demonstrates three computed patterns in one form: arithmetic, ternary condition, and SUM aggregate",
    "Arithmetic: `#/properties/x * #/properties/y + #/properties/z` — standard operator precedence (* before +)",
    "Ternary: `#/properties/x > 10 ? #/properties/y : #/properties/z` — returns y if x>10, else z",
    "SUM: `SUM(#/properties/arr/c3)` — sums the c3 column across all array rows",
    "Computed fields render as read-only inputs that update automatically as users enter data",
    "The `description` field holds the expression — it doubles as tooltip text in some renderers"
  ]
}
